    "When the chair of the university's art history department, <a href=\"/dvorakm\">Max Dvo\u0159\u00e1k</a>, died unexpectedly in 1922, Schlosser was nominated as his replacement.": [],
    "Schlosser, initiallly urged <a href=\"/pinderw\">Wilhelm Pinder</a> to the position but ultimately accepted the <em>Ordinarius</em> appointment himself.": [
