    "Schlosser was succeeded by a former student, <a href=\"/sedlmayrh\">Hans Sedlmayr</a>.": [],
    "Assertions that Schlosser was a member of the Nazi party appear untrue--perhaps based a photo of him wearing a swastika pin, required of all faculty in 1938 (Johns, 2012).": [],
