    "The second half of Schlosser's life was devoted to the study of <a href=\"/ghibertil\">Lorenzo Ghiberti</a>, whose influence Schlosser had come to appreciate through the study of primary texts.": [],
    "As an art historian, Schlosser eschewed the specialist's mantel.": [],
